			<div class="content" id="post-content-2280667">
									

<p>I'm sorry about the year-old necro, but I feel this is worth addressing:<br />
The document claims that the Bathysphere was lowered into the Tonga Trench, which is 10,882 metres at its deepest point. New Zealand is located 2.2&#160;km away from the Tonga Trench, but there's nothing in the document to say that 096 was ever contained in New Zealand. Tonga is only 260&#160;km away from the trench, which fits neatly in the three-digit number the document gives us.</p>

							</div>

								
